results.deck: Amaze entertainment is a developer mostly known for porting liscensed games to various platforms.
results.description: Amaze Entertainment is a member of the independent group of design studios known as Foundation 9. They are most known for their movie-based titles and handheld games. They work in the same building as Griptonite Games. The current building they use once also housed testing facilities for the Mars Rover.
